            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Nymphis <lb n="2"/>sacrum <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ors</ex></expan> II <expan><abbr>Raet</abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>ivium</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>R</abbr><ex>omanorum</ex></expan> cui <lb n="5"/>pr<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>eest</abbr></expan> <lb n="6"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost">S</supplied>exti<lb break="no" n="7"/><supplied reason="lost">us V</supplied>ictor <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost">prae</supplied>fect</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan></supplied> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aeta</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Auf der linken Nebenseite eine ascia und ein Futteral für Opfermesser, auf der rechten Nebenseite urceus und patera. (B): Jacobi: Z. 7: Vi]ctor; Mattern: Z. 8/9: [pre]fect/[u]s [v(otum)] s(olvit).</p>
            </div>
